<title>UK: BT Effecten sets warrants on Novartis.</title>
<headline>BT Effecten sets warrants on Novartis.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>BT Effecten GmbH has issued one million American-style cal warrants on shares of Novartis AG, lead manager Bankers Trust International said.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    2,200 CHF		 PREMIUM	16.53 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     1.49 DEM		  GEARING	16.25 TIMES</p>
<p> MATURITY DATE   17.JUL.98		 PAYDATE	04.JUN.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   FFT/BER/HAM/STUT/DUES</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  1,994.5 CHF (FOREX 120.20 CHF/DEM)</p>
<p>-- Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
